channel.desc: Comedy 2004 Jon is a pet lover who owns a dog named Odie and a cat named Garfield. Unexpectedly, when this dog disappears, Garfield takes the responsibility to search for and find it. Breckin Meyer, Jennifer Love Hewitt, Stephen Tobolowsky, Evan Arnold, Bill Murray, Peter Hewitt, Jim Davis, Joel Cohen, Alec Sokolow.
